Require agentgrep

Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui-filter.gif
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui-filter.mp4
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui-filter.webm

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Source docs/_static/demos/vhs/_preamble.tape

Sleep 500ms
Type "agentgrep ui"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "cache OR retry"
Enter
Sleep 2200ms
Down
Sleep 350ms
Type "codex"
Sleep 1500ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 350ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 350ms
Ctrl+C
Wait
Sleep 800ms
